dct_title_s: Prishtina, hartë e qytetit 1:10 000 : hartë rrugore dhe turistike : hartë e qytetit 1:10 000 = Prishtina, city map 1:8 000 : road and touristic map : city map 1:10 000
dct_description_sm: Street map showing principal buildings, generalized land use, and cemeteries by religious groups. Includes note, street index, and airline advertisements. Some sites are shown pictorially. On verso: Prishtina sourrunding [surroundings] = Prishtina me rrethinë. Includes notes, street index, and color illustrations.
